    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、そんなに引き留められたら仕方ないですね～\nあとちょっとだけ付き合ってあげます～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ if you insist on keeping me that much‚ I can’t help it~\nI’ll hang out with you just a little longer~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（いや、引き留めたのはこころなんだが……まぁいいか）\n（次は順番から考えて……こころの話か？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Well‚ she’s the one who kept me here… oh well.）\n（Next‚ judging by the order… is it Kokoro’s story?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 19.6749423425
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "おお、正解です\nさすがはこころのファンですね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ correct!\nAs expected of Kokoro’s fan~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "しれっと心を覗かないでくれ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t casually read my mind like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4137634357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 27.3113362869
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "でもBIG4のこころのプライベートを\n知りたいだなんて……\nなかなかの大物ですね～{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But wanting to know about BIG4’s Kokoro’s private life—\nthat’s quite something…\nYou’re quite the big shot‚ {user}-san~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 35.2716532311
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
