      "text": "でもそんなこころでも\nアメリカでのツアーは凄く大変だったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But even Kokoro herself—\nthe tour in America was really tough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
