      "text": "国内ツアー以上に体力も気力も使うので疲れるし\nその土地その土地で求められることが違って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It took even more physical and mental energy than domestic tours‚ so it was exhausting‚\nand every place had different expectations.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_feststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "feststage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.073263558
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
