      "text": "パフォーマンスから、何から何まで柔軟に変えて\n一杯一杯になりかけちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I had to adapt everything—from performances to every detail—\nand I almost hit my limit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5511026155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_feststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "feststage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.4090233568
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよな……\n言葉の壁も大きそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I can imagine…\nThe language barrier must have been tough too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.1000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_feststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "feststage-00-noon",
