      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 77.2878678326
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "でもこころだって何もしてない訳じゃないですよ～\nちゃーんと英語だって勉強してるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it’s not like I didn’t do anything myself~\nI’ve been studying English properly too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.7333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 87.3223768318
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、kanaさんに教えてもらったこのアプリで！\n{user}さんに特別に披露してあげますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "See‚ with this app kana-san taught me!\nI’ll give you a special demonstration‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.4666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 95.1527623261
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
