      "text": "ふーあーゆー？　おー！　まいねーむいずこころ～\nうぃあおーるれでぃふれんずふれんず～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Hoo-are-yuu? Oooh! Mai ne-mu iz Kokorooo~”\n“Wee aa al-ready friends friends~”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.9666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "いぇーい！　あいむじゃぱにーずとっぷあいどる！\nかわいいあいどる～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Ya-y! I'm Japanese top idol!\"\n\"Kawaii idol~\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
