    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……こころらしいフレンドリーな言葉選びだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu… that’s a very Kokoro-like friendly choice of words.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.0841030841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（そういえばkanaさん達もラスベガスで「自分達は）\n（日本のトップアイドルだ」って言っていたような……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Come to think of it‚ kana and the others also said in Las Vegas‚）\n（“We’re Japan’s top idols‚” if I recall…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 124.2284052139
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "あっ{user}さん、今バカにしましたね？\n見てて下さい、次会った時はペラペラになってますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san‚ you just made fun of me‚ didn’t you!?\nJust watch! Next time we meet‚ I’ll be fluent!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.8333282471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "これからツアーを巡るいろんな国でも、こころの\nBIG英会話4を駆使して世界を魅了してやりますよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And in all the countries we visit next‚ Kokoro’s\n“BIG English Conversation 4” will charm the world~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.0666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 142.2258670097
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "さて、次はいよいよお待ちかねのあの話！\n心の準備はいいですか……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now then‚ it’s finally time for that story you’ve been waiting for!\nAre you ready…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.0666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "今回のアメリカツアーで、一番印象的だったこと……\n{user}さんにこそ聞いてほしいお話です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The most memorable thing from this American tour…\nIt’s something I especially want you to hear‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.6666615804,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5066.671752900021,
          "startTime": 160.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 158.9042646016
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺に聞いてほしい話……？\nん……こころ、その音は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A story you want me to hear…?\nHm… Kokoro‚ that sound…",
